				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Halsin approaches you the morning after you celebrated your victory over the goblins. He now turns to the matter of your tadpole and how you might cure yourself - there is no quick solution, however. He tells you it'll be necessary to travel to a dangerous new region, and joins you at your camp to provide support."
